    <description>A lightweight .NET Framework 4.7.2 library for validating JWT tokens including expiration checks and optional signature verification (HS256, RS256). Perfect for quick pre-validation checks and full JWT validation.</description>
    <releaseNotes>
v1.1.0 (2026-01-XX)
- NEW: JWT signature verification support (HS256 and RS256)
- NEW: VerifySignature() method for HMAC-SHA256 verification
- NEW: VerifySignatureRS256() method for RSA-SHA256 verification
- NEW: GetAlgorithm() method to detect JWT algorithm
- NEW: Base64UrlEncode() method
- NEW: JwtVerificationResult class for detailed results
- IMPROVED: Complete signature verification documentation
- 100% backward compatible with v1.0.x

v1.0.1 (2026-01-XX)
- Documentation improvements
- Clean namespace (Johan.Common)
- Verified no company references
- NuGet package enhancements (README and LICENSE display)
- All 58+ tests passing

v1.0.0 (2026-01-XX)
- Initial release
- JWT expiration validation with clock skew support
- Base64URL decoding
- Thread-safe implementation
- 58+ unit tests with ~100% API coverage
    </releaseNotes>
